## Secrets Management

Secrets are managed using **{{if eq (printf "%s" .Secrets.Type) "sealed-secrets"}}Sealed Secrets{{else if eq (printf "%s" .Secrets.Type) "external-secrets"}}External Secrets Operator{{else}}SOPS{{end}}**. See [SECRETS.md](SECRETS.md) for details.

## Bootstrap Process

To bootstrap a new cluster:

{{- if eq (printf "%s" .Controller.Type) "argocd"}}

```bash
# 1. Apply the bootstrap manifests
kubectl apply -k bootstrap/argocd/

# 2. Wait for ArgoCD to be ready
kubectl -n argocd rollout status deployment argocd-server

# 3. ArgoCD will pick up apps/_root.yaml and sync everything else
```
{{- else}}

```bash
# 1. Apply the Flux controllers
kubectl apply -f https://github.com/fluxcd/flux2/releases/download/v{{.Controller.Version}}/install.yaml

# 2. Wait for Flux to be ready
kubectl -n flux-system rollout status deployment source-controller
kubectl -n flux-system rollout status deployment kustomize-controller

# 3. Apply the root sync (update the Git repo URL first)
kubectl apply -f apps/_root.yaml
```
{{- end}}
